			<td><a href="FeatDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Sprightly Armor"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Sprightly Armor*</a></td><td>Dex 13, base attack bonus +11 or fighter level 8th, armor training class feature, proficiency with light armor.</td><td>Gain your armor's enhancement bonus to initiative</td>
